        "zh": "影片製作流程介紹<br>After Effects的介紹<br>認識AE的Transform動畫<br>遮罩(Mask)的操作與運用與內建特效使用<br>3D Layer的使用與<br>燈光鏡頭的運用<br>Keying去背<br>文字特效<br>粒子特效<br>Track Motion特效整合",
        "en": "1.\tIntroduction to the film production process<br>2.\tIntroduction to After Effects<br>3.\tMeet AE's Transform animation<br>4.\tMask operation and use and built-in effects<br>5.\tThe use of 3D Layer and<br>6.\tUse of light lens<br>7.\tKeying to back<br>8.\tText effects<br>9.\tParticle effect<br>10.\tTrack Motion effects integration<br>"
